						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone kept outside the Saṅkaraliṅga temple.</p>						

						<p>A.D. 1001.</p>						

						<p>This damaged and worn out inscription is dated in the cyclic year Śaka 923, Plava, Chaitra, śu. 10, Sunday corresponding to A.D. 1001, April 6, Sunday. Seems to record the death of hero (name lost).</p>						

